<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ooniversary on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/tags/ooniversary/</link><description>Recent content in Ooniversary on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 09 Dec 2022 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ooni.github.io/tags/ooniversary/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>OONI Community Video</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/post/ooni-community-video/</link><pubDate>Fri, 09 Dec 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/post/ooni-community-video/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;We are happy to celebrate OONI&amp;rsquo;s 10th anniversary together with our
amazing community, who have been at the heart of our work over the past
decade.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, we are excited to share a &lt;strong&gt;new video with OONI community
members&lt;/strong&gt;, where they discuss how OONI has been useful to their work,
while sharing what they would like to see OONI do in the future.&lt;/p&gt;
